nodes.bodyText: @xstefank - how did you decide on this value (and the user.name above)? Is it (and the line above) required to set this for the action to work
nodes.diffHunk:
@@ -0,0 +1,40 @@
+name: LRA test
+
+on:
+  push:
+    branches: [ master ]
+    paths:
+      - "rts/lra/**"
+  pull_request:
+    branches: [ master ]
+    paths:
+      - "rts/lra/**"
+  # Allows you to run this workflow manually from the Actions tab
+  workflow_dispatch:
+
+jobs:
+  lra-test:
+
+    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
+
+    steps:
+    - uses: actions/checkout@v2
+    - name: Set up JDK 1.8
+      uses: actions/setup-java@v1
+      with:
+        java-version: 1.8
+    - name: Cache local Maven repository
+      uses: actions/cache@v2
+      with:
+        path: ~/.m2/repository
+        key: ${{ runner.os }}-maven-${{ hashFiles('**/pom.xml') }}
+        restore-keys: |
+          ${{ runner.os }}-maven-
+    - name: LRA test
+      run: |
+        git config --global user.name "jbosstm"
+        git config --global user.email "jbosstm@users.noreply.github.com"
